        <mxCell id="legend" value="Flujo: Usuario → ALB:&lt;externo&gt; → Target Group (port = interno) → Container:&lt;interno&gt;&#xa;Puertos externos del ALB (listeners): ui=80, catalog=8001, cart=8002, checkout=8003, orders=8004, admin=3001&#xa;Puertos internos (PORT env = target group = escucha del container): catalog=8080, orders=8080, cart=8002, checkout=8003, ui=3000, admin=3001&#xa;Fuente: infrastructure/modules/ecs/main.tf (service_internal_ports / service_alb_ports)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F8F9FA;strokeColor=#D2D6DC;fontColor=#232F3E;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=10;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
